---
title: Penne with Sausage, Corn, and Zucchini On (or Off) the Grill
description: Celebrate the arrival of warmer temperatures with this summery, fully loaded pasta. It balances al dente penne with some salad-like greens and tomatoes, then takes things over the top with smoky charred sausage and zucchini you can prepare on or off the grill—just the thing to kick back on the patio with and dig in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w22-r5-cb368eff.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/w22-r5-305e9ef9.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
servings: 2
cuisine: North America
